items.name: AREA
desc: The graphic is scaled to fill the whole surrounding area.

items.name: LEFT_BOTTOM
desc: The graphic is located in the bottom left corner.

items.name: LEFT_MIDDLE
desc: The graphic is located in the middle of the left edge.

items.name: LEFT_TOP
desc: The graphic is located in the top left corner.

items.name: MIDDLE_BOTTOM
desc: The graphic is located in the middle of the bottom edge.

items.name: MIDDLE_MIDDLE
desc: The graphic is located at the center of the surrounding object.

items.name: MIDDLE_TOP
desc: The graphic is located in the middle of the top edge.

items.name: NONE
desc: No column or page break is applied.
This value specifies that a location is not yet assigned.

items.name: RIGHT_BOTTOM
desc: The graphic is located in the bottom right corner.

items.name: RIGHT_MIDDLE
desc: The graphic is located in the middle of the right edge.

items.name: RIGHT_TOP
desc: The graphic is located in the top right corner.

items.name: TILED
desc: The graphic is repeatedly spread over the surrounding object like tiles.
